item.title: Tikinang's 2nd 🧠
item.description: Hi entities! …and welcome to my 2nd 🧠, my digital garden 🌱🪴, my personal knowledge-base 📖… whoami? call myself “Tikinang” (for whatever reason) 🤙 live in Prague, Czech Republic 🇨🇿 work as back-end Go developer 💻🦫 universal knowledge hunter 🏹📚 BJJ enthusiast and competitor 🥋🏆 enjoy… grabbing a beer with friends 🍻 sports of all kinds ⚽🏀🏊‍♂️🎾 startup world, investing, green technology 🌍💰🌳 [[notes/Résumé|Résumé]] for head-hunters.
